{"rappelCountMax":9,"description":"<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><p>Well known canyon amongst non canyoning people as it ends immediately in the city of Montreux. Short and easy, definitely a good option for initiations.\n<\/p>\n<meta property=\"mw:PageProp\/toc\" \/>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Approach\">Approach<\/h2><\/div>\n<p>There is a path going along the canyon pretty much all the time. Enter at the bridge at 810m above sea level.\n<\/p>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Descent\">Descent<\/h2><\/div>\n<p>First part has 4 rappels then another one a bit further down. After this, better go back to the hiking trail and enter again more than 2km further, from the bridge at a height of 535m above sea level. There the canyon gets slightly more interesting, but is also really short.\n<\/p>\n<style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r1062633282\">@media all and (max-width:720px){.mw-parser-output .content .thumb>div:not(.thumbinner){display:flex;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;align-content:flex-start;flex-direction:column}}body.skin-vector .mw-parser-output div.thumb>div:not(.thumbinner){font-size:94%;text-align:center;overflow:hidden;min-width:100px}body.skin-minerva .mw-parser-output div.thumb>div:not(.thumbinner){margin:0 auto;max-width:100%!important}<\/style> \n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div style=\"display:table;\">\n<span class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:Error mw:File\/Frameless\">\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Exit\">Exit<\/h2><\/div>\n<p>When being under the big Highway bridges, walk up to the path before the river reaches the first buildings.\n<\/p>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Red_tape\">Red tape<\/h2><\/div>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Beta_sites\">Beta sites<\/h2><\/div>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http:\/\/swisscanyon.ch\/canyons\/lista-ch-west.htm?Chauderon\">SwissCanyon.ch<\/a> &#160;: Chauderon<\/li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http:\/\/swestcanyon.ch\/www_swisscanyon_ch_fichiers\/lista-ch-west.htm?Chauderon\">SwestCanyon.ch<\/a> &#160;: Chauderon<\/li><\/ul>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Trip_reports_and_media\">Trip reports and media<\/h2><\/div>\n<div class=\"mw-heading mw-heading2\"><h2 id=\"Background\">Background<\/h2><\/div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw‐api‐ext.codfw.main‐6779cc57fc‐74czk\nCached time: 20240914192117\nCache expiry: 2592000\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: [show‐toc]\nCPU time usage: 0.032 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.039 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 114\/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 710\/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 55\/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8\/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0\/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0\/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 529\/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.002\/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 606898\/52428800 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0\/400\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   28.882      1 -total\n100.00%   28.882      1 Template:Pic\n 52.56%   15.180      1 Template:Str_number\/trim\n-->\n<\/div>","version":"2a3e203f9183394913c242325e6a331807ff7557335be70ad0d5fe942d705b40","geojson":null,"vehicle":null,"rappelLongestMeters":15,"quality":2.3,"name":"Chauderon","timeRating":"II","latitude":46.4487,"rappelCountMin":9,"longitude":6.9454,"shuttleSeconds":null,"url":"https:\/\/ropewiki.com\/Chauderon","waterRating":"C1","months":["Jun","Jul","Aug","Sep","Oct","Nov"],"id":27566,"technicalRating":3,"riskRating":null,"permit":"No"}